## Technical SEO Requirements
### Title Tag Optimization
- **Length**: 50-60 characters for optimal display in SERPs
- **Keyword Placement**: Primary keyword within first 60 characters
- **Brand Integration**: Include brand name when appropriate
- **Uniqueness**: Ensure unique titles across all pages
- **Emotional Triggers**: Use power words to improve click-through rates

### Meta Description Optimization
- **Length**: 150-160 characters for full display in SERPs
- **Keyword Integration**: Include primary keyword naturally
- **Call-to-Action**: Include compelling CTA when appropriate
- **Value Proposition**: Clearly communicate content value
- **Uniqueness**: Ensure unique descriptions across all pages

### Heading Structure (H1-H6)
- **H1**: Single H1 per page with primary keyword
- **H2**: Main section headings with secondary keywords
- **H3-H6**: Subsection headings for content organization
- **Keyword Distribution**: Natural keyword integration in headings
- **Hierarchy**: Logical content flow and structure

### Content Optimization
