- **LSI Keywords**: Include semantically related terms naturally
- **Readability**: Maintain Flesch-Kincaid score of 60-80
- **Content Length**: Minimum 300 words, optimal 800-2000 words
- **Internal Linking**: 2-5 internal links per 1000 words

